item.title: Garden of Eatin': Carrots with Jon Glover & Marisa Pinson
item.description: Jon Glover (@gloveboxx) and Marisa Pinson (@marisapinson) of On Brand join the 'boys to talk the Hollywood Arby's, line cutting, and the history behind "Animal Style" before talking all things carrots in the final episode of The Garden of Eatin': Veggie Table: The Green Gobblin'.
